---
title: Double Sweet Chilli Chicken Bites & Rainbow Salad with Crispy Shallots
description: This classic seasoning blend goes nicely with succulent chicken, and paired with a sweet chilli sauce makes a perfect match! Rest it on a cushy pillow of carrot salad to serve, and add a sprinkle of crispy shallots for some flair!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*

